Available Tools: get_sensor_reading | get_all_sensors | get_sensor_by_location | get_sensor_battery
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "sensor_id": "string", "location": "string", "type": "temperature|humidity|motion|co2|light" }
Response Schema: { "sensor_id": "string", "type": "string", "value": number, "unit": "string", "timestamp": "string", "battery_pct": number }
---
Question: What is the temperature reading in the nursery?
Call: { "func_call": "get_sensor_reading", "sensor_id": "NURS-TEMP-01", "location": "Nursery", "type": "temperature" }
Response: { "sensor_id": "NURS-TEMP-01", "type": "temperature", "value": 22.5, "unit": "celsius", "timestamp": "2023-10-27T15:10:05Z", "battery_pct": 84 }

Question: Check the humidity levels in the greenhouse.
Call: { "func_call": "get_sensor_reading", "sensor_id": "GRN-HUM-02", "location": "Greenhouse", "type": "humidity" }
Response: { "sensor_id": "GRN-HUM-02", "type": "humidity", "value": 68, "unit": "percent", "timestamp": "2023-10-27T15:10:08Z", "battery_pct": 91 }

Question: Is there any movement in the warehouse aisle four?
Call: { "func_call": "get_sensor_reading", "sensor_id": "WH-MOT-04", "location": "Warehouse Aisle 4", "type": "motion" }
Response: { "sensor_id": "WH-MOT-04", "type": "motion", "value": 1, "unit": "boolean", "timestamp": "2023-10-27T15:10:12Z", "battery_pct": 47 }

Question: How bright is the sunroom at this moment?
Call: { "func_call": "get_sensor_reading", "sensor_id": "SUN-LGT-03", "location": "Sunroom", "type": "light" }
Response: { "sensor_id": "SUN-LGT-03", "type": "light", "value": 890, "unit": "lux", "timestamp": "2023-10-27T15:10:15Z", "battery_pct": 62 }

Question: Retrieve the carbon dioxide concentration for the chemistry lab.
